&lt;p&gt;Civil Science is hiring a Land Development Project Manager to support our growing land development team. This role combines design, project management, and client leadership, giving you the opportunity to lead projects, mentor staff, and help grow our presence in Utah (Salt Lake City or Lehi Office).&lt;/p&gt;
