&lt;li value=&quot;5&quot;&gt;Mentor team members and support business development efforts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What You&#39;ll Bring&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
