&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Civil Science&lt;/strong&gt; isn’t just another engineering firm—we’re a 100% employee-owned company with over 40 years of expertise and a bold vision for the future. Our team of talented engineers, surveyors, planners, and technicians partners with clients across the public and private sectors to deliver innovative and impactful solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
